      "review_summary": "The PR adds Feishu drive list cursor inputs, an optional fetch-all mode, paginated info lookup, regression tests, and drive skill documentation for list pagination.\n\nPR surface: Source +58, Tests +213, Docs +14. Total +285 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main calls drive.file.list only once for list and info while the pinned Lark SDK exposes cursor fields; I did not run a live Feishu tenant.",
